untdid2379JsonType.title: Date and Time format codes for JSON representation.
untdid2379JsonType.description:
This code list is based on UNTDID 2379. It is adjusted to take JSON date and time representation into account.
# The following abbreviations are used
* 'C' – Century
 * 'Y' – Year
 * 'M' – Month
 * 'D' – Day
 * 'h' – Hour
 * 'm' – Minute
 * 's' – Second
 * 'w' – Week
 * 'T' – Time zone offset separator (+/-/Z) 
 
 * 'A' – 10 day period within a month of a year
 * 'B' – 1: First half month; 2: second half month
 * 'E' – Week of a month
 * 'G' – Working days
 * 'H' – Half month
 * 'I' – 1-9: Shift in a day
 * 'K' – 1-5: First to fifth week in a month
 * 'M' – Trimester: A period of three months
 * 'N' – 1-7: Numeric representation of the day (Monday = 1, Sunday = 7)
 * 'P' – A period of 4 months
 * 'Q' – Quarter
 * 'RR' – 00-99: Time period
 * 'S' – Semester
 *
  * Hyphens and additional character in a format string are kept. According to ISO 8601 a slash is used to separate time spans.
 # Codes from UNTDID 2379 and their representation in JSON
 * '2' – is represented as 'date' format
 * '3' – is represented as 'date' format
 * '4' – is represented as 'date' format
 * '5' – is represented as 'date-time' format
 * '6' – is represented as 'CCYY-MM-B'

id.title: Exchanged_ Document. Identification. Identifier
id.description: The unique identifier of this exchanged document.

typeCode.title: Exchanged_ Document. Type. Code
typeCode.description: The code specifying the type of exchanged document.

issueDateTime.title: Exchanged_ Document. Issue. Date Time
issueDateTime.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value for the issuance of this exchanged document.

purposeCode.title: Exchanged_ Document. Purpose. Code
purposeCode.description: A code specifying the purpose of this exchanged document, such as request or reminder.

referenceReferencedDocument.title: Exchanged_ Document. Reference. Referenced_ Document
referenceReferencedDocument.description: Other documents referenced by this exchanged document.

recipient.title: Exchanged_ Document. Recipient. Trade_ Party
recipient.description: A trade party that receives this exchanged document.

geographicalCoordinateType.title: Geographical Coordinate. Details
geographicalCoordinateType.description: A set of geographical coordinates of a specific point such as the longitude, latitude and altitude.

latitude.title: Geographical Coordinate. Latitude. Measure
latitude.description: The measure of the latitude as an angular distance north or south from the Equator meridian to the meridian of a specific place for this geographical coordinate (Reference ISO 6709).

longitude.title: Geographical Coordinate. Longitude. Measure
longitude.description: The measure of the longitude as an angular distance east or west from the Greenwich meridian to the meridian of a specific place (Reference ISO 6709).

isOrHasLatitudeDirection.title: Geographical Coordinate. Latitude Direction. Indicator
isOrHasLatitudeDirection.description: The indication of whether the latitude compass direction from the Equator meridian to the meridian of a specific place is North (+) or South (-)  (Reference ISO 6709).

isOrHasLongitudeDirection.title: Geographical Coordinate. Longitude Direction. Indicator
isOrHasLongitudeDirection.description: The indication of whether the longitude as a compass direction from the Greenwich meridian to the meridian of a specific place is East (+) or West (-) for this geographical coordinate (Reference ISO 6709).

systemId.title: Geographical Coordinate. System. Identifier
systemId.description: The unique identifier of the reference system used for measuring a geographical coordinate.

logisticsLocationType.title: Logistics_ Location. Details
logisticsLocationType.description: A logistics related physical location or place.

id.title: Logistics_ Location. Identification. Identifier
id.description: A unique identifier for this logistics related location, such as a United Nations Location Code (UNLOCODE) or GS1 Global Location Number (GLN).

name.title: Logistics_ Location. Name. Text
name.description: A name, expressed as text, of this logistics related location.

physicalGeographicalCoordinate.title: Logistics_ Location. Physical. Geographical Coordinate
physicalGeographicalCoordinate.description: Geographical coordinate information for this logistics related location.

logisticsSealType.title: Logistics_ Seal. Details
logisticsSealType.description: A device used to secure an object and protect it from unauthorized entry or tampering during transport or other logistics operations.

id.title: Logistics_ Seal. Identification. Identifier
id.description: A unique identifier for this logistics seal.

typeCode.title: Logistics_ Seal. Type. Code
typeCode.description: The code specifying the type of logistics seal.

conditionCode.title: Logistics_ Seal. Condition. Code
conditionCode.description: A code specifying a condition of this logistics seal.

sealingPartyRoleCode.title: Logistics_ Seal. Sealing Party Role. Code
sealingPartyRoleCode.description: The code specifying the role of the party responsible for the sealing of this logistics seal.

logisticsStatusType.title: Logistics_ Status. Details
logisticsStatusType.description: The information relevant to a condition or a position related to logistics.

conditionCode.title: Logistics_ Status. Condition. Code
conditionCode.description: The code specifying this logistics status condition [UNECE Recommendation 24].

referenceDateTime.title: Logistics_ Status. Reference. Date Time
referenceDateTime.description: The reference date, time, date time or other date time value for this logistics status.

description.title: Logistics_ Status. Description. Text
description.description: The textual description of this logistics status.

reasonCode.title: Logistics_ Status. Reason. Code
reasonCode.description: A code specifying a reason for this logistics status [UNECE Recommendation 24].

reason.title: Logistics_ Status. Reason. Text
reason.description: A reason, expressed as text, for this logistics status.

specifiedLogisticsLocation.title: Logistics_ Status. Specified. Logistics_ Location
specifiedLogisticsLocation.description: A location specified for this logistics status.

logisticsTransportEquipmentType.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Details
logisticsTransportEquipmentType.description: A piece of equipment used to hold, protect or secure cargo for logistics purposes.

id.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Identification. Identifier
id.description: The unique identifier of this piece of logistics transport equipment.

categoryCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Category. Code
categoryCode.description: The code specifying the category for this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as container or trailer.

characteristicCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Characteristic. Code
characteristicCode.description: The code specifying the characteristic or characteristics of this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as the ISO 6346 transport equipment size and type code.

characteristic.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Characteristic. Text
characteristic.description: The characteristic or characteristics, expressed as text, of a piece of logistics transport equipment, such as its size and type.

supplierPartyRoleCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Supplier Party Role. Code
supplierPartyRoleCode.description: The code specifying the role of the party responsible for supplying this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as the carrier or the buyer.

usedCapacityCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Used Capacity. Code
usedCapacityCode.description: The code specifying the used capacity of this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as full or empty.

operationalStatusCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Operational Status. Code
operationalStatusCode.description: The code specifying the operational status for this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as to be repaired or to be shifted.

transportMovementStatusCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Transport Movement Status. Code
transportMovementStatusCode.description: The code specifying the transport movement status for this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as for export, for import, or for transhipment.

legalStatusCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Legal Status. Code
legalStatusCode.description: The code specifying the legal status of this piece of logistics transport equipment with respect to a specific law such as the "Container Convention Code".

haulageArrangementCode.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Haulage Arrangement. Code
haulageArrangementCode.description: The code specifying the arrangement for the haulage of this piece of logistics transport equipment.

information.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Information. Text
information.description: Information, expressed as text, for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

sealQuantity.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Seal. Quantity
sealQuantity.description: The quantity of seals for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

containedConsignmentQuantity.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Contained Consignment. Quantity
containedConsignmentQuantity.description: The number of consignments contained in this piece of logistics transport equipment.

carrierAssignedBookingId.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Carrier Assigned Booking_ Identification. Identifier
carrierAssignedBookingId.description: A carrier assigned booking identifier for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

isOrHasSealed.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Sealed. Indicator
isOrHasSealed.description: The indication of whether or not this piece of logistics transport equipment is sealed.

loadedDangerousGoods.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Loaded. Transport_ Dangerous Goods
loadedDangerousGoods.description: Dangerous goods loaded into this piece of logistics transport equipment.

affixedLogisticsSeal.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Affixed. Logistics_ Seal
affixedLogisticsSeal.description: A seal affixed to this piece of logistics transport equipment.

attachedTransportEquipment.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Attached. Attached_ Transport Equipment
attachedTransportEquipment.description: Transport equipment attached to this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as ropes or refrigeration units.

carriedAssociatedTransportEquipment.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Carried. Associated_ Transport Equipment
carriedAssociatedTransportEquipment.description: A piece of transport equipment carried on this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as a container placed on a rail wagon.

containedAssociatedTransportEquipment.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Contained. Associated_ Transport Equipment
containedAssociatedTransportEquipment.description: A piece of transport equipment contained within this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as a pallet.

loadingEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Loading. Transport_ Event
loadingEvent.description: The loading event for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

unloadingEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Unloading. Transport_ Event
unloadingEvent.description: The unloading event for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

positioningEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Positioning. Transport_ Event
positioningEvent.description: A positioning event specifying when and where this piece of logistics transport equipment will be, or has been, positioned, i.e. delivered and available for pick-up.

pickUpEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Pick-Up. Transport_ Event
pickUpEvent.description: A pick-up event specifying when and where this piece of logistics transport equipment will be, or has been, collected, i.e. picked-up by the carrier.

operating.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Operating. Trade_ Party
operating.description: The party that operates this piece of logistics transport equipment.

carrier.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Carrier. Trade_ Party
carrier.description: A carrier party for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

specifiedLogisticsTransportMeans.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Specified. Logistics_ Transport Means
specifiedLogisticsTransportMeans.description: A transport means specified for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

reportedLogisticsStatus.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Reported. Logistics_ Status
reportedLogisticsStatus.description: A status reported for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

consolidationEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Consolidation. Transport_ Event
consolidationEvent.description: A consolidation event specifying when and where this piece of logistics transport equipment will be, or has been, stuffed.

deliveryEvent.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Delivery. Transport_ Event
deliveryEvent.description: A delivery event for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

associatedReferencedDocument.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Associated. Referenced_ Document
associatedReferencedDocument.description: A referenced document associated with this piece of logistics transport equipment.

applicableNote.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Applicable. Note
applicableNote.description: A note providing information applicable to this piece of logistics transport equipment.

actualRoute.title: Logistics_ Transport Equipment. Actual. Transport_ Route
actualRoute.description: An actual route for this piece of logistics transport equipment.

logisticsTransportMeansType.title: Logistics_ Transport Means. Details
logisticsTransportMeansType.description: The devices used to convey goods or other objects from place to place during logistics cargo movements.

id.title: Logistics_ Transport Means. Identification. Identifier
id.description: An identifier of this logistics means of transport, such as the International Maritime Organization number of a vessel.

name.title: Logistics_ Transport Means. Name. Text
name.description: The name, expressed as text, of this logistics means of transport.

measurementType.title: Measurement. Details
measurementType.description: An amount, size, or extent as established by measuring.

actual.title: Measurement. Actual. Measure
actual.description: An actual measure for this measurement.

noteType.title: Note. Details
noteType.description: A textual or coded description, such as a remark or additional information.

contentCode.title: Note. Content. Code
contentCode.description: A code specifying the content of this note.

content.title: Note. Content. Text
content.description: A content, expressed as text, of this note.

subjectCode.title: Note. Subject. Code
subjectCode.description: A code specifying the subject of this note.

referencedDocumentType.title: Referenced_ Document. Details
referencedDocumentType.description: Written, printed or electronic matter that is referenced.

typeCode.title: Referenced_ Document. Type. Code
typeCode.description: The code specifying the type of referenced document.

id.title: Referenced_ Document. Identification. Identifier
id.description: A unique identifier for this referenced document.

issueDateTime.title: Referenced_ Document. Formatted_ Issue. Date Time
issueDateTime.description: The formatted date or date time for the issuance of this referenced document.

referenceDateTime.title: Referenced_ Document. Reference. Date Time
referenceDateTime.description: The reference date or date time for this referenced document.

tradeAddressType.title: Trade_ Address. Details
tradeAddressType.description: The location at which a particular trade related organization or person may be found or reached.

postcodeCode.title: Trade_ Address. Postcode. Code
postcodeCode.description: A code specifying the postcode of this trade address.

streetName.title: Trade_ Address. Street Name. Text
streetName.description: A name, expressed as text, of a street or thoroughfare for this trade address.

cityName.title: Trade_ Address. City Name. Text
cityName.description: A name, expressed as text, of the city, town or village of this trade address.

countryId.title: Trade_ Address. Country. Identifier
countryId.description: The unique identifier of a country for this trade address.

countrySubDivisionName.title: Trade_ Address. Country Sub-Division Name. Text
countrySubDivisionName.description: A name, expressed as text, of the sub-division of a country for this trade address.

tradeContactType.title: Trade_ Contact. Details
tradeContactType.description: A person or a department that acts as a point of contact with another person or department in a trading relationship.

personName.title: Trade_ Contact. Person Name. Text
personName.description: A name, expressed as text, of this trade contact person.

departmentName.title: Trade_ Contact. Department Name. Text
departmentName.description: A name, expressed as text, of the department to which this trade contact belongs within an organization.

telephoneUniversalCommunication.title: Trade_ Contact. Telephone. Universal_ Communication
telephoneUniversalCommunication.description: Telephone communication information for this trade contact.

mobileTelephoneUniversalCommunication.title: Trade_ Contact. Mobile_ Telephone. Universal_ Communication
mobileTelephoneUniversalCommunication.description: The mobile telephone communication information for this trade contact.

emailURIUniversalCommunication.title: Trade_ Contact. Email_ URI. Universal_ Communication
emailURIUniversalCommunication.description: The email URI communication information for this trade contact.

tradePartyType.title: Trade_ Party. Details
tradePartyType.description: An individual, a group, or a body having a role in a trade business function.

id.title: Trade_ Party. Identification. Identifier
id.description: A unique identifier of this trade party.

name.title: Trade_ Party. Name. Text
name.description: A name, expressed as text, for this trade party.

definedTradeContact.title: Trade_ Party. Defined. Trade_ Contact
definedTradeContact.description: A trade contact defined for this trade party.

postalTradeAddress.title: Trade_ Party. Postal. Trade_ Address
postalTradeAddress.description: The postal address for this trade party.

dangerousGoodsType.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Details
dangerousGoodsType.description: Goods which may contain a substance which poses risks to people and/or the environment during transportation which is regulated by dangerous goods regulations.

undgIdCode.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. UNDG Identification. Code
undgIdCode.description: The code specifying the unique United Nations Dangerous Goods (UNDG) number assigned to these transported dangerous goods.

regulationCode.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Regulation. Code
regulationCode.description: The code specifying a regulation applicable to these transported dangerous goods.

technicalName.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Technical Name. Text
technicalName.description: A technical name, expressed as text, for these transported dangerous goods.

emsId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. EMS. Identifier
emsId.description: The unique transport emergency procedure (EMS) identifier applicable for these transported dangerous goods.

tremId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. TREM. Identifier
tremId.description: The unique TRansport EMergency (TREM) card identifier for these transported dangerous goods.

upperPartOrangeHazardPlacardId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Upper Part Orange Hazard Placard. Identifier
upperPartOrangeHazardPlacardId.description: The unique upper part of the orange hazard placard identifier for these transported dangerous goods.

lowerPartOrangeHazardPlacardId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Lower Part Orange Hazard Placard. Identifier
lowerPartOrangeHazardPlacardId.description: The unique lower part of the orange hazard placard identifier for these transported dangerous goods.

mfagId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. MFAG. Identifier
mfagId.description: The unique Medical First Aid Guide (MFAG) identifier for these transported dangerous goods.

packagingDangerLevelCode.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Packaging Danger Level. Code
packagingDangerLevelCode.description: The code specifying the level of danger that the packaging of these dangerous goods must cover for transport purposes.

hazardTypeCode.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Hazard Type. Code
hazardTypeCode.description: A code specifying the type of hazard for these transported dangerous goods.

hazardClassificationId.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Hazard Classification. Identifier
hazardClassificationId.description: The unique identifier of a hazard class applicable to these transported dangerous goods as defined by the relevant governing regulation authority.

isOrHasPollutant.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Pollutant. Indicator
isOrHasPollutant.description: The indication of whether or not these transported dangerous goods have a pollutant content.

isOrHasMarinePollutant.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Marine_ Pollutant. Indicator
isOrHasMarinePollutant.description: The indication of whether or not these transported dangerous goods have a marine pollutant content.

flashpointTemperatureMeasurement.title: Transport_ Dangerous Goods. Flashpoint Temperature. Measurement
flashpointTemperatureMeasurement.description: A measurement of the flashpoint temperature of these transported dangerous goods.

eventType.title: Transport_ Event. Details
eventType.description: A significant occurrence or happening during transport.

typeCode.title: Transport_ Event. Type. Code
typeCode.description: The code specifying the type of transport event.

estimatedOccurrenceDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Estimated_ Occurrence. Date Time
estimatedOccurrenceDateTime.description: The estimated date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

actualOccurrenceDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Actual_ Occurrence. Date Time
actualOccurrenceDateTime.description: The actual date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

scheduledOccurrenceDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Scheduled_ Occurrence. Date Time
scheduledOccurrenceDateTime.description: The scheduled date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

requestedOccurrenceDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Requested_ Occurrence. Date Time
requestedOccurrenceDateTime.description: The requested date, time, date time, or other date time value of the occurrence of this transport event.

scheduledArrivalRelatedDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Scheduled Arrival_ Related. Date Time
scheduledArrivalRelatedDateTime.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the scheduled arrival related to this transport event.

actualArrivalRelatedDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Actual Arrival_ Related. Date Time
actualArrivalRelatedDateTime.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the actual arrival related to this transport event.

scheduledDepartureRelatedDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Scheduled Departure_ Related. Date Time
scheduledDepartureRelatedDateTime.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the scheduled departure related to this transport event.

actualDepartureRelatedDateTime.title: Transport_ Event. Actual Departure_ Related. Date Time
actualDepartureRelatedDateTime.description: The date, time, date time or other date time value of the actual departure related to this transport event.

occurrenceLogisticsLocation.title: Transport_ Event. Occurrence. Logistics_ Location
occurrenceLogisticsLocation.description: The logistics location where this transport event occurs.

routeType.title: Transport_ Route. Details
routeType.description: A way or course taken from one location to another for the purpose of transporting cargo and or passengers.

itineraryStopEvent.title: Transport_ Route. Itinerary Stop. Transport_ Event
itineraryStopEvent.description: An itinerary stop event for this transport route, such as a port call in a vessel schedule.

universalCommunicationType.title: Universal_ Communication. Details
universalCommunicationType.description: The exchange of thoughts, messages, or information, as universally exchanged by speech, signals, writing, or behaviour between persons and/or organizations.

uri.title: Universal_ Communication. URI. Identifier
uri.description: The Uniform Resource Identifier (URI), such as a web or an email address, for this universal communication.

completeNumber.title: Universal_ Communication. Complete Number. Text
completeNumber.description: The text string of characters that make up the complete number for this universal communication.
